# A shout of exultation.

===Verb===
{{en-verb|pres_3sg2=halloes}}

# {{lb|en|intransitive}} To shout, or to call with a loud voice.
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To chase while shouting "hallo!"
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To cry "hallo" (to someone).
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To shout (something).

